  "text": "Next we explored the possibility that the improved R 2 values from the SimCVR fit relative to the BP fit were due to the timedynamics of the system that could be captured with a simple transfer function (TF fit). Based on published methods for transfer function analysis on cerebral autoregulation [CITATION_1] , we chose to fit a 2nd order continuous-time system transfer function G of the form",
